      "raw_text": "AUBURN, n. Y, Dec. 23.-The\nrecent visit of Mrs. .Emmeline Pank-\nhurst here, where an audience of\nWells college girls heard her speak\non Votes for Women resulted to-\nday in the formation of a woman\nsuffrage society at the college, with\nthe sanction of Dean Plutti. Last\nyear Wells college was unanimously\nopposed to woman suffrage."
    }
